    },
    {
      x:700, y:880,
      label:'The Hedgerow',
      desc:'Where the Old Forest meets the Enclosure Fields. Not a clean line. A zone of contested boundary, constantly being pushed back and occasionally recovering. The enclosers call this wasteland. The commons knows it as the most biodiverse strip on the map.',
